        "created_at": "2018-09-24T06:02:03.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"145956\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Was 2017 good in BOJO?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yes, very nice vintage: 2011 springs to mind as an analogy, or a mix of 2015 and 2016, with some wines tending more in one direction or the other. Though there was hail once again, Fleurie being hit especially hard, the wines are generally less marked by it.</p>",
